history.content:
The annual Health Hackathon is back, and we are calling all Engineers, Designers, and Innovators!

Whether you live to improve human health, tackle medical/health issues with innovation, or simply want a collaborative space to share your inventive creativity, this hackathon is meant for you!

APPLY FOR ISPE HACKING HUMAN HEALTH HERE BY MARCH 11th!
https://tinyurl.com/ISPEH32020

Visit the Hacking Human Health website at this link: https://ispe.berkeley.edu/hackathon/

We welcome and encourage students of all backgrounds and skill sets to join us! 🙂 NO EXPERIENCE NECESSARY
history.subject: Health Hackathon (Hacking Human Health) Hosted by ISPE
